<br />

<br />
The mass media and academia, in the name of tolerance and political correctness, promote the idea to the American public that Islam, by and large, is peaceful in its message. Wrong. For instance, the recent revelations about the University of North Carolinas freshmen assignment of selections of the Koran. As always, academia includes only the touchy-feely selections. The University omitted the selections about how it is the duty of Muslims to kill Christians, Jews and other infidels. Also censored were the sections concerning holy war as a vital importance to the cause of Islam. Islam is being sanitized and the American people duped into believing that Islam is a peaceful religion. The complete teachings of Islam and the stark differences between Islam and Western Civilization are being eliminated. As we approach the next phase in the war against Jihadistan, the war against Saddam Hussein, we must approach it in the same way as any total war. We can debate the strategy to achieve victory, but the objective is clear: the destruction of Jihadistan and the protection of American liberty.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
